Technical Milestone: Integrated Google Sheets API to create a persistent storage layer for all mentor-student interactions.

Data Mapping: Configured automated logging for Timestamp, Sender Metadata, Inbound Inquiry, and AI Output.

Business Intelligence: Established a foundation for trend analysis and curriculum optimization based on historical student data.

Workflow Optimization: Positioned the logging module as a middle-ware step to ensure data is captured before final egress (email reply).
